@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
        <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
            <h4 class="mb-0">Introduction</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>Welcome to our Car Insurance platform! Your privacy is very important to us, and we are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding your personal data.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
        <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
            <h4 class="mb-0">Information We Collect</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>We collect personal information from you when you register for an account, make a claim, or interact with our services. This may include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Personal identification information (name, email, phone number, etc.)</li>
                <li>Vehicle information (make, model, registration details, etc.)</li>
                <li>Claim details (incident description, damages, etc.)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We may also collect non-personal information such as cookies, IP addresses, and browser data to improve the user experience.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
        <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
            <h4 class="mb-0">How We Use Your Information</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>We use your information to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Provide personalized car insurance quotes and manage your policy</li>
                <li>Process and track claims</li>
                <li>Improve our website and services</li>
                <li>Send you important updates and promotional offers (if you have opted-in)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Your personal information will not be sold or shared with third parties unless required by law or for the purpose of fulfilling services related to your account.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
        <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
            <h4 class="mb-0">Data Security</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>We take appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction. However, no data transmission over the internet can be guaranteed as 100% secure, so we cannot ensure complete security of your data.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
        <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
            <h4 class="mb-0">Your Rights</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>You have the right to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Access your personal information</li>
                <li>Request corrections or updates to your information</li>
                <li>Request deletion of your personal data (subject to legal requirements)</li>
                <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
            </ul>
            <p>To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at <a href="">safetrail@gmail.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
        <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
            <h4 class="mb-0">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices, legal requirements, or the introduction of new services. We will notify users of any significant changes through the website or email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-5">
        <p>Thank you for choosing SafeTrail. Your privacy and security are our top priority. If you have any questions or concerns, please feel free to contact us.</p>
    </div>
</div>